Some updates to compile sketches for NodeMCU with newer versions of Arduino IDE and refactored for Python3: Martin Boller

To flash the firmware:

# apt-get install esptool
# git clone http://github.com/martinboller/BUSSide.git
# esptool --port /dev/ttyUSB0 write_flash 0x00000 BUSSide/FirmwareImages/*.bin

# cd BUSSide/Client
# ./busside.py /dev/ttyUSB0

To build from source:
Include library EssSoftwareSerial (Sketch -> Include Library -> select EspSoftwareSerial from list)
